# Plan 14: Video Integration & Player

## Goal

Create the "Videos" page and admin management for videos.

## Tasks

- [x] Create `app/videos/page.tsx`.
- [x] Create `app/admin/videos/page.tsx`.
- [x] Implement a `VideoCard` component:
  - [x] Use **ShadCN Card**.
  - [x] Use **ShadCN AspectRatio** (16:9) for the thumbnail.
  - [x] Add a play overlay.
- [x] Create a video player modal:
  - [x] Use **ShadCN Dialog**.
  - [x] Support YouTube/Vimeo embeds and native HTML5 video.
- [x] Fetch videos from the database.
- [x] Implement video management in the admin panel (add links, upload thumbnails).
